name: Angry dope owls by Ayodele Trademan

metadata.name: Angry GenG owl    (leader)
metadata.description: A whimsical, magical fairy tale about a group of disgruntled owls who live peacefully together until some ambitious members form a coup. The power struggle leads to mysterious and dangerous consequences for all involved; full of danger and intrigue, it will keep you on the edge of your seat!
